#: reservations/services/admin_workflows.py:118
msgid "Published terms are required."
msgstr "Se requieren términos publicados."

#: reservations/services/admin_workflows.py:135
msgid ""
"A complimentary settlement cannot leave an amount due. Enter zero, apply "
"enough customer credit, or adjust the charge first."
msgstr ""
"Una liquidación de cortesía no puede dejar un importe pendiente. Introduzca "
"cero, aplique suficiente crédito del cliente o ajuste primero el cargo."

#: reservations/services/admin_workflows.py:150
msgid ""
"Explain this settlement method so the commercial decision remains auditable."
msgstr ""
"Explique este método de liquidación para que la decisión comercial siga "
"siendo auditable."

#: reservations/services/admin_workflows.py:165
msgid "A complimentary payment requires a zero outstanding balance."
msgstr "Un pago de cortesía requiere un saldo pendiente de cero."

#: reservations/services/admin_workflows.py:207
#: reservations/services/transfers.py:431
msgid "Published pre-reservation terms are required."
msgstr "Se requieren los términos de pre-reserva publicados."

#: reservations/services/admin_workflows.py:232
#: reservations/services/transfers.py:462
msgid "Published reservation terms are required."
msgstr "Se requieren los términos de reserva publicados."

#: reservations/services/admin_workflows.py:265
#: reservations/services/admin_workflows.py:477
msgid "Online payment requires a registered customer."
msgstr "El pago en línea requiere un cliente registrado."

#: reservations/services/admin_workflows.py:270
msgid "The pre-reservation amount cannot be negative."
msgstr "El importe de la pre-reserva no puede ser negativo."

#: reservations/services/admin_workflows.py:274
msgid ""
"A pre-reservation requires a published dog price so the future reservation "
"deposit can be calculated. Create a direct reservation instead and enter the"
" agreed amount."
msgstr ""
"Una pre-reserva requiere un precio publicado del perro para poder calcular "
"el futuro depósito de reserva. Cree una reserva directa e introduzca el "
"importe acordado."

