msgid ""
"Record the customer terms acceptance before recording an offline pre-"
"reservation payment."
msgstr ""
"Registre la aceptación de los términos del cliente antes de registrar un "
"pago de pre-reserva fuera de línea."

#: reservations/services/admin_workflows.py:301
msgid ""
"Published reservation terms are required because a paid staff pre-"
"reservation is accepted automatically."
msgstr ""
"Se requieren condiciones de reserva publicadas porque una pre-reserva pagada"
" creada por el personal se acepta automáticamente."

