msgid "The reservation amount cannot be negative."
msgstr "El importe de la reserva no puede ser negativo."

#: reservations/services/admin_workflows.py:485
msgid "Customer credit must be between zero and the reservation amount."
msgstr ""
"El crédito del cliente debe estar entre cero y el importe de la reserva."

