msgid "The selected credit belongs to another customer."
msgstr "El crédito seleccionado pertenece a otro cliente."

#: reservations/services/admin_workflows.py:513
msgid ""
"Record the customer terms acceptance before recording an offline reservation"
" payment."
msgstr ""
"Registre la aceptación de los términos del cliente antes de registrar un "
"pago de reserva fuera de línea."

#: reservations/services/admin_workflows.py:520
msgid "Reservation validity must be between 1 and 168 hours."
msgstr "La validez de la reserva debe estar entre 1 y 168 horas."

#: reservations/services/admin_workflows.py:606
msgid "Applied to a direct reservation by staff."
msgstr "Aplicado a una reserva directa realizada por el personal."

