msgid "Close or reconcile active online payments before completing the sale."
msgstr ""
"Cierre o concilie los pagos en línea activos antes de completar la venta."

#: reservations/services/admin_workflows.py:742
msgid "The final sale price cannot be negative."
msgstr "El precio final de la venta no puede ser negativo."

#: reservations/services/admin_workflows.py:753
msgid ""
"The value already settled exceeds the final sale price. Resolve the excess "
"as a refund or customer credit first."
msgstr ""
"El valor ya liquidado supera el precio final de la venta. Resuelva el "
"excedente como reembolso o crédito al cliente primero."

#: reservations/services/admin_workflows.py:761
msgid "Customer credit cannot exceed the final outstanding balance."
msgstr "El crédito al cliente no puede superar el saldo final pendiente."

#: reservations/services/admin_workflows.py:779
msgid "Applied to the final animal sale."
msgstr "Aplicado a la venta final del animal."

#: reservations/services/admin_workflows.py:950
msgid ""
"Record the customer acceptance of the current pre-reservation terms before "
"settling this stage."
msgstr ""
"Registre la aceptación del cliente de las condiciones actuales de pre-"
"reserva antes de liquidar esta etapa."

