msgid ""
"Record the customer acceptance of the current reservation terms before "
"settling this stage."
msgstr ""
"Registre la aceptación del cliente de las condiciones actuales de reserva "
"antes de liquidar esta etapa."

#: reservations/services/closures.py:47
msgid "Refund and credit amounts cannot be negative."
msgstr "Los montos de reembolso y crédito no pueden ser negativos."

#: reservations/services/closures.py:51
msgid ""
"Refund and credit cannot exceed the value currently available in this "
"process."
msgstr ""
"El reembolso y el crédito no pueden superar el valor disponible actualmente "
"en este proceso."

#: reservations/services/closures.py:71
msgid ""
"At least the customer credit already used in this process must return to "
"customer credit."
msgstr ""
"Al menos el crédito del cliente ya utilizado en este proceso debe devolverse"
" al crédito del cliente."

#: reservations/services/closures.py:83
msgid "The requested refund exceeds refundable real payments."
msgstr "El reembolso solicitado supera los pagos reales reembolsables."

#: reservations/services/closures.py:103
msgid "Returned because the animal workflow was closed."
msgstr "Devuelto porque el flujo de trabajo del animal se cerró."

#: reservations/services/closures.py:158 reservations/services/payment.py:862
msgid "The target refund percentage must be between 0 and 100."
msgstr "El porcentaje objetivo de reembolso debe estar entre 0 y 100."

#: reservations/services/closures.py:211
msgid "Wait for pending refunds before closing this process."
msgstr "Espera los reembolsos pendientes antes de cerrar este proceso."

#: reservations/services/closures.py:261
msgid "The requested refund could not be allocated to payments."
msgstr "El reembolso solicitado no pudo asignarse a los pagos."

